        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:11:47 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:11:47 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Julian Resendiz, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/28/tick-bites-kill-16-in-chihuahua.webp" alt="Tick bites kill 16 in Chihuahua"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tick bites kill 16 in Chihuahua</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Summer not only brings hot temperatures that can dehydrate humans; it’s also prime time for the reproduction of dangerous bugs, according to medical experts.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/28/tick-bites-kill-16-in-chihuahua/"  >(Julian Resendiz, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 22:28:49 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 22:28:49 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="DAVID A. LIEB, Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/27/missouri-governor-says-new-public-aid-plan-in-the-works-for-chiefs-royals-stadiums.webp" alt="Missouri governor says new public aid plan in the works for Chiefs, Royals stadiums"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Missouri governor says new public aid plan in the works for Chiefs, Royals stadiums</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      JEFFERSON CITY, Mo. (AP) — Missouri Gov. Mike Parson said Thursday that he expects the state to put together an aid plan by the end of the year to try to keep the Kansas City Chiefs and Royals from being lured across state lines to new stadiums in Kansas.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/27/missouri-governor-says-new-public-aid-plan-in-the-works-for-chiefs-royals-stadiums/"  >(DAVID A. LIEB, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 01:46:02 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 01:46:02 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Caroline Vakil, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/28/trump-says-he-will-not-block-access-to-mifepristone.webp" alt="Trump says he will not block access to mifepristone"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump says he will not block access to mifepristone</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former President Trump said Thursday he would not block access to the abortion pill mifepristone if he returned to the White House.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/28/trump-says-he-will-not-block-access-to-mifepristone/"  >(Caroline Vakil, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:35:59 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:35:59 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="WILL WEISSERT, Associated Press, PHL 17">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/28/heres-why-it-would-be-tough-for-democrats-to-replace-joe-biden-on-the-presidential-ticket.webp" alt="Here's why it would be tough for Democrats to replace Joe Biden on the presidential ticket"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Here's why it would be tough for Democrats to replace Joe Biden on the presidential ticket</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WASHINGTON (AP) — President Joe Biden 's halting debate performance on Thursday night has led some in his own party to begin questioning whether he should be replaced on the ballot before November. There is no evidence Biden is willing to end his campaign.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/28/heres-why-it-would-be-tough-for-democrats-to-replace-joe-biden-on-the-presidential-ticket/"  >(WILL WEISSERT, Associated Press, PHL 17)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 23:15:16 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 23:15:16 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Jim Vertuno, Associated Press, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/27/former-uvalde-school-police-chief-and-officer-indicted-over-robb-elementary-response-reports-say.webp" alt="Former Uvalde police chief indicted over response to Robb Elementary shooting"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Former Uvalde police chief indicted over response to Robb Elementary shooting</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Uvalde’s former school police chief has been booked and released from jail following a grand jury investigation into the police response during the Robb Elementary School shooting in 2022.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/27/former-uvalde-school-police-chief-and-officer-indicted-over-robb-elementary-response-reports-say/"  >(Jim Vertuno, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 21:42:29 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 21:42:29 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Joshua Hoggard, KLAS, CBS News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/27/bakery-behind-viral-maga-cookie-now-offers-biden-themed-option.webp" alt="Bakery behind viral MAGA cookie now offers Biden-themed option"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Bakery behind viral MAGA cookie now offers Biden-themed option</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      "At the end of the day maybe it is now political. Maybe it’s unavoidable. But everyone needs to know, we are not the ones who pushed it there.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/27/bakery-behind-viral-maga-cookie-now-offers-biden-themed-option/"  >(Joshua Hoggard, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:34:57 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:34:57 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JONATHAN J. COOPER, Associated Press, PHL 17">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/28/trump-and-biden-spar-on-economy-after-skipping-handshake-at-start-of-debate.webp" alt="Trump and Biden mix it up over policy and each other in a debate that turns deeply personal"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump and Biden mix it up over policy and each other in a debate that turns deeply personal</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      PHOENIX (AP) — They passed on a handshake at the start, and from there President Joe Biden and former President Donald Trump went right to mixing it up on policy — and each other — in their first 2024 presidential debate on Thursday night.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/28/trump-and-biden-spar-on-economy-after-skipping-handshake-at-start-of-debate/"  >(JONATHAN J. COOPER, Associated Press, PHL 17)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
