  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/24/princess-anne-injured-concussed-in-incident-buckingham-palace-says.webp" alt="Princess Anne hospitalized with minor injuries after 'incident,' Buckingham Palace says"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Princess Anne hospitalized with minor injuries after 'incident,' Buckingham Palace says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Buckingham Palace says Princess Anne has sustained minor injuries and concussion following an incident on the Gatcombe Park estate on Sunday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/24/princess-anne-injured-concussed-in-incident-buckingham-palace-says/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:04:04 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:04:04 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="SYLVIE CORBET, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/28/france-is-facing-an-election-like-no-other-heres-how-it-works-and-what-comes-next.webp" alt="France is facing an election like no other. Here's how it works and what comes next"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">France is facing an election like no other. Here's how it works and what comes next</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      PARIS (AP) — French voters are being called to the polls on Sunday for an exceptional moment in their political history: the first round of snap parliamentary elections that could see the country’s first far-right government since the World War II Nazi occupation — or no majority emerging at all.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/28/france-is-facing-an-election-like-no-other-heres-how-it-works-and-what-comes-next/"  >(SYLVIE CORBET, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:36:53 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:36:53 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/27/thai-banks-top-suppliers-financial-services-burmas-military-un-expert-says.webp" alt="Thai banks are leading financial backers of Burma's military, UN expert says"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Thai banks are leading financial backers of Burma's military, UN expert says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Thai banks have become the main supplier of international financial services for Burma’s military government, according to a report by a U.N. expert on human rights.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/27/thai-banks-top-suppliers-financial-services-burmas-military-un-expert-says/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 00:57:58 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 00:57:58 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JAMEY KEATEN, Associated Press, KREX 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/world/2024/06/28/ballot-box-binge-votes-loom-in-coming-days-from-mongolia-to-iran-to-britain-in-a-busy-election-year.webp" alt="Ballot box binge: Votes loom in coming days from Mongolia to Iran to Britain in a busy election year"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ballot box binge: Votes loom in coming days from Mongolia to Iran to Britain in a busy election year</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Even in a busy year of elections around the world, the next few days stand out. Over the next week, voters go to the polls in fledgling democracies like Mauritania and Mongolia, the Islamic Republic of Iran and in stalwart democracies — former imperial powers — Britain and France. In the U.S.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/28/ballot-box-binge-votes-loom-in-coming-days-from-mongolia-to-iran-to-britain-in-a-busy-election-year/"  >(JAMEY KEATEN, Associated Press, KREX 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/tech/">Technology</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:57:05 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:57:05 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="CIO">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/tech/2024/06/27/demystifying-ai-understanding-weak-and-strong-ai.webp" alt="Demystifying AI: Understanding weak and strong AI"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Demystifying AI: Understanding weak and strong AI</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Artificial Intelligence (AI) is one of the most transformative technologies of our time, yet it remains widely misunderstood.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/27/demystifying-ai-understanding-weak-and-strong-ai/"  >(CIO)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
