    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tesla has faced these legal and regulatory actions over environmental issues at its Fremont factory</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Tesla has faced multiple legal and regulatory actions over environmental issues involving its Fremont factory in recent years.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/26/tesla-has-faced-these-legal-and-regulatory-actions-over-environmental-issues-at-its-fremont-factory/"  >(Ethan Baron, The Mercury News)</a>
