           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Indonesia Refuses to Pay $8 Million Ransom After Cyberattack on National Data Center</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Jakarta, Indonesia - A hacking group compromised the country's national data center, demanding an $8 million ransom, but the government has refused to pay, taking a tough stance against cybercriminals.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/25/indonesia-wont-pay-an-8-million-ransom-after-a-cyberattack-compromised-its-national-data-center/"  >(NINIEK KARMINI, Associated Press, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
