    <h3 itemprop="headline">Sharks reportedly had interest in Canucks forward before trade to Blackhawks</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The San Jose Sharks reportedly had some interest in bringing in Ilya Mikheyev from the Vancouver Canuck
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/27/sharks-reportedly-had-interest-in-mikheyev-before-trade-to-chicago/"  >(Curtis Pashelka, The Mercury News)</a>
