           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Jazz draft Duke All-American Kyle Filipowski in second round</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SALT LAKE CITY (ABC4 Sports) - It was a painful night for Kyle Filipowski, as he had to wait at the Barclay's Center through the entire first round without hearing his name called.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/28/jazz-select-duke-all-american-kyle-filipowski-in-second-round/"  >(Dana Greene, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:15:18 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:15:18 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
