           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Jazz select Cody Williams with 10th pick in NBA Draft</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BROOKLYN, N.Y. (ABC4 Sports) - The Utah Jazz drafted one of the most athletic player in the NBA Draft, selecting Colorado swingman Cody Williams with the 10th overall pick. In his only season at Colorado, Williams averaged 11.9 points, 3.0 rebounds and 1.9 assists per game.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/27/jazz-select-cody-williams-with-10th-pick-in-nba-draft/"  >(Dana Greene, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
