           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Cities receive aid to help plan for climate change</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The state funding will help Minnesota communities plan for the impacts of climate change. Many cities have outdated stormwater management systems that can’t handle extreme rainfalls.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/26/cities-receive-state-aid-to-help-plan-for-climate-change-extreme-weather/"  >(Kirsti Marohn, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
