  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:52:39 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:52:39 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="CALVIN WOODWARD, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/28/debate-watchers-in-the-biden-and-trump-camps-seem-to-agree-on-something-biden-had-a-bad-night.webp" alt="Debate-watchers in the Biden and Trump camps seem to agree on something. Biden had a bad night"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Debate-watchers in the Biden and Trump camps seem to agree on something. Biden had a bad night</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WASHINGTON (AP) — “Oh, Joe." That gasp, from patrons at a Chicago bar when President Joe Biden first stumbled verbally in his debate with Donald Trump, spoke for a lot of Americans on Thursday night.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/28/debate-watchers-in-the-biden-and-trump-camps-seem-to-agree-on-something-biden-had-a-bad-night/"  >(CALVIN WOODWARD, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:56:58 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:56:58 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Nicole Rogers, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
