           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Presidential debate: What does it mean for the Tampa Bay voter?</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The nation watched President Joe Biden and Former President Donald Trump square off in the first debate of this election cycle.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/28/presidential-debate-what-does-it-mean-for-the-tampa-bay-voter/"  >(Nicole Rogers, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 25 Jun 2024 19:50:56 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 25 Jun 2024 19:50:56 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
