           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">House Republicans propose contempt for Biden ghostwriter</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The House Judiciary Committee is set to weigh a contempt referral for President Biden’s ghostwriter, seeking to tee up criminal charges after failing to secure audio of the president’s interviews.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/25/house-republicans-to-consider-holding-biden-ghostwriter-in-contempt/"  >(Rebecca Beitsch, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 21:45:00 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 21:45:00 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press and NPR Staff, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/27/president-joe-biden-and-former-president-donald-trump-first-2024-presidential-debate.webp" alt="President Joe Biden and former President Donald Trump clash in first 2024 presidential debate"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">President Joe Biden and former President Donald Trump clash in first 2024 presidential debate</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Biden and former President Donald Trump faced off in the first presidential debate of the 2024 general election Thursday night in Atlanta, kicking off a new phase of the presidential race as the matchup remains extremely tight.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/27/president-joe-biden-and-former-president-donald-trump-first-2024-presidential-debate/"  >(The Associated Press and NPR Staff, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 23:59:26 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 27 Jun 2024 23:59:26 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Kevin Accettulla, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/27/desantis-signs-bill-designating-jimmy-buffett-memorial-highway.webp" alt="DeSantis signs bill designating Jimmy Buffett Memorial Highway"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">DeSantis signs bill designating Jimmy Buffett Memorial Highway</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Gov. Ron DeSantis on Thursday signed a bill to designate Florida A1A -- which runs through beaches along the Atlantic coast, as "Jimmy Buffett Memorial Highway.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/27/desantis-signs-bill-designating-jimmy-buffett-memorial-highway/"  >(Kevin Accettulla, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:36:39 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:36:39 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Cassie Buchman, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/26/how-trump-biden-rfk-jr-are-polling-ahead-of-the-first-debate.webp" alt="How Trump, Biden, RFK Jr. are polling ahead of the first debate"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">How Trump, Biden, RFK Jr. are polling ahead of the first debate</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      While they might not be thrilled about the candidates, many voters are planning to pay attention to the debate.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/26/how-trump-biden-rfk-jr-are-polling-ahead-of-the-first-debate/"  >(Cassie Buchman, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
